CLCD control register : 0x80049000
1) Disable the Lcd power  and wait at least 20 MS
   0x80049000 bit 22 set to 0
2)disable the Lcd
  0x80049000 bit 0 set  to 0
3) stop the CL clock
  0x80050030 bit 10 set  to 0
4)disable Vee and Backlight
 GPIO PE bit 1 & 2 set to 0

